RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2009-1757. In re Adoption of P.A.C.

Hamilton App. No. C-081149, 184 Ohio App.3d 88, 2009-Ohio-4492. Reported at 126 Ohio St.3d 236, 2010- Ohio-3351, 933 N.E.2d 236. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.
